						<p>This inscription records the gift of this pillar by Kīraṇ Dēvaṅguḍaiyān Piṟai Śūḍuvān Kuṇṟameṟindāṉ <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Suṭṭiyāḷaviṭṭa Chōḻamūvēndavēḷāṉ, who was one of the revenue officers of the king (<hi rend="italic">Perumāḷ puravariyār</hi>).</p>						

